Similar to what we're seeing, this repro has hundreds of re-renders, and the number is nondeterministic.

<img width="105" alt="Screenshot 2024-05-23 at 11 06 11â€¯AM" src="https://github.com/facebook/react/assets/4248263/7871459c-de6e-4880-933a-da83498d4720">

